nodes.text: Gree was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories, in the grid square L-2 of the Standard Galactic Grid.

Gree was first introduced in the current Star Wars canon in the galactic map of 2016 Fantasy Flight Games' roleplaying game boxed set Star Wars: The Force Awakens Beginner Game. The planet Gree was originally introduced in the Star Wars Legends continuity in the The Gree Enclave, an article written by Timothy O'Brien and published in West End Games' Star Wars Adventure Journal 8 in 1995.
